{"tid":133633,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"轉router 求推介","createTime":"2017-02-24T18:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T06:15:27.000Z","uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21ce42338e39c2592d1aeaaf19619e4811e52986","tid":133633,"uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"屋企啱啱由100mb 轉左1000mb<br />\n本身隻router 唔夠用要轉想問下巴打們有咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外因為我屋企個間隔比較特別<br />\n個router擺廳要穿4幅牆入去主人(爹娘)房<br />\n想問下<br />\n- 直接買一個勁嘅router可以穿到入去<br />\n- 買一個router 加x個repeater <br />\n- 買2個router一個做main一個做ap mode<br />\n邊樣會好啲<br />\n<br />\n全部野加埋大約有$1200 budget<br />\n<br />\n利伸 小弟唔係好識 但係爹娘要我搞唯有試下<br />\n求各位幫下細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163edcb9dda3bbe222a9e8cbf6700f93153c8383","tid":133633,"uid":2129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:03:00.000Z","msg":"4幅牆 1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b72d9ed588e10e449557a98f07464c3c2b6715","tid":133633,"uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4幅牆 1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁大約要幾多先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係冇乜概念 求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf9a06b147a4a83eab76fe7598115e1e803ab82","tid":133633,"uid":2129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4幅牆 1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁大約要幾多先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係冇乜概念 求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先一個食到1000mb既router 連登仔推既68u 又好 <br />\nr7000都好都800-900<br />\n重點係你有四幅牆 點會加repeater 係都homeplug<br />\n我就一定唔會買tp link<br />\n係都買netgear plw1000<br />\n四幅牆起碼兩對<br />\n你預3000budget就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedfaa51445c9808515060897b845d944ec2e254","tid":133633,"uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"講漏咗小小<br />\n其實我成間屋都有拉好晒線<br />\n即係每間房都有LAN線可以駁出廳<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係用homeplug<br />\n係每間房插一個AP連住個router咁得唔得?<br />\n想問下啲access point會係幾錢<br />\n咁做會唔會平啲"},{"pid":"2530e64af6a3e4b6a7d9d44d7615ac0b95d5ea19","tid":133633,"uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"118bef22691e6542d3e2a6ad132b357062274e9c","tid":133633,"uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:49:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"024e503a411ec7ea967e3ec8928ed3d5c88c6982","tid":133633,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"行晒1000既router都唔止$1200"},{"pid":"48505de2742133c08db7889e22c3e16b536d87b2","tid":133633,"uid":22061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行晒1000既router都唔止$1200</blockquote><br />\n但係